					Products					

Doctor John Young has incorporated the latest Biochemical, Physiological and Nobel Prize winning protocols to create a program and products designed to address the causes of many chronic illnesses.
Below is a list of the key products offered and available and Young Foundational Health Center designed to help each patient build a strong foundation at the cellular level, enabling the body to restore itself and achieve peak performance.
Be sure to refer to our Product & Supplement Glossary for more information recommended products and supplements recommended by and available at Young Foundational Health Center.
We look forward to assisting you in your pursuit of getting healthy and staying healthy!
Young Power Protein
This protein is a super concentrated why protein. The milk used to create our protein is derived from cows that are grass fed year round on natural pastures that are pesticide and chemical-free. It is the optimal nutritional supplement to assist in antioxidant production, healthy immune system function, cellular repair, complete amino acid supplementation, muscle growth and weight management.
A-B Balance Drops
These drops raise the pH of Liquid. This makes it easier for hemoglobin to give oxygen to a cell, which increases vitality. They help the body maintain the acid/base balance in the blood as well as other tissues. When acid levels rise just a little the body must rob alkaline minerals from the bones (osteoporosis) if it can’t produce enough bicarbonate to do the job. These drops will help the body to do just that.
Flax Seed and Cod Liver Oil 
Flaxseed oil contains both omega-3 and omega-6 fatty acids, which are needed for health. Flaxseed oil contains the essential fatty acid alpha-linolenic acid (ALA), which the body converts into eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA) and docosahexaenoic acid (DHA), the omega-3 fatty acids found in fish oil. Cod liver oil is a great source of vitamins A and D and also has omega-3 fatty acids like EPA and DHA that help in treating/preventing various medical conditions like cardiovascular disease, cancer, type 1 diabetes, neurological illnesses like Alzheimer’s and autism, arthritis, and asthma. Put together, these two oils are the perfect combination to set you up for a healthy body.
Fruit of the Spirit
Fruit of the Spirit is a whole fruit puree rich in Anti-Oxidants and Alkalizing Minerals. 1-2 ounces a day supplies your body with the energizing and healing nutrients required for human health and vitality. This highly concentrated liquid is a unique blend of 16 super-fruits & herbs, including Biblical herbs Frankincense and Myrrh. These are the same Whole Foods and Dead Sea minerals that provide powerful Anti-Oxidants, Minerals and Vitamins while helping to maintain a healthy range of alkalinity in the body. One ounce of Fruit of the Spirit delivers the nutritional equivalent of 5 servings of Fresh Fruits & Vegetables, and twice a day provides all the nutrients you need for better health and wellness with sustained energy naturally.
Young Health Shake (Budwig Cocktail) 
The drink is very anti-inflammatory. It contains a lot of Omega 3 oils, which are incorporated into the cell membrane so the oxygen concentration of the cell increases, which translates into increased vitality. The cocktail has 25-30 grams of protein in each serving. Unless oil is emulsified into a protein, your body will find it hard to use the omega 3 oils. This cocktail is really the science from the 1931 Nobel Prize in medicine; remodeling a cell membrane so it is more permeable to Oxygen, and yet supplies protein to help remake the outer coat of the cell membrane.
*All of these ingredients put together in one or two Power Shakes a day can dramatically change the health and wellness of your body, by simply getting to the root of the problem and providing you with all the essential nutrients your cells need to create a healthy body.
You can still purchase Dr. Young’s products even though you are not a patient at his office. Please go to YoungHealth.com.View our Return Policy. 
















